criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  confirmed diagnosis of COPD by spirometry (post-bronchodilator FEV1/FVC < 0.70);

          -  at least 2 self-reported exacerbations in the previous 12 months, i.e. a change for ≥
             2 consecutive days in either ≥ 2 major symptoms (dyspnea, sputum purulence, sputum
             amount) or any 1 major symptom plus any ≥ 1 minor symptoms (colds, wheeze, sore
             throat, cough).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  severe co-morbid conditions that prohibit participation;

          -  unable to communicate in the Dutch language;

          -  difficulties using a smartphone;
